{"tid":948250,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"BBC中文網一篇報導 \"2018年中美關係大事記\", 出現幾小時後又消失咗?!","createTime":"2018-12-20T01:57:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-20T02:28:22.000Z","uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b3f11d659d2306311facc27de950d6067ff91cd5","tid":948250,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T01:57:47.000Z","msg":"2018年中美關係大事記<br />\nBBC 中文网-5 小時前<br />\n1月：美國眾議院通過《台灣旅行法》草案，其後經參議院無異議通過、總統特朗普簽字，正式生效。《台灣旅行法》為美台官員互訪解禁，但觸碰被認為是 ...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com/search?q=%222018%E5%B9%B4%E4%B8%AD%E7%BE%8E%E9%97%9C%E4%BF%82%E5%A4%A7%E4%BA%8B%E8%A8%98%22&amp;tbm=nws&amp;source=univ&amp;tbo=u&amp;sa=X&amp;ved=2ahUKEwi66qPYpq3fAhVC_GEKHeTuDXkQt8YBKAF6BAgAEAY&amp;biw=895&amp;bih=370\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Fsearch%3Fq%3D%25222018%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E7%25BE%258E%25E9%2597%259C%25E4%25BF%2582%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E4%25BA%258B%25E8%25A8%2598%2522%26tbm%3Dnws%26source%3Duniv%26tbo%3Du%26sa%3DX%26ved%3D2ahUKEwi66qPYpq3fAhVC_GEKHeTuDXkQt8YBKAF6BAgAEAY%26biw%3D895%26bih%3D370&d=bxRmApblJ2GFsDTLoFA1i26kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=767de2f3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/search?q=%222018%E5%B9%B4%E4%B8%AD%E7%BE%8E%E9%97%9C%E4%BF%82%E5%A4%A7%E4%BA%8B%E8%A8%98%22&amp;tbm=nws&amp;source=univ&amp;tbo=u&amp;sa=X&amp;ved=2ahUKEwi66qPYpq3fAhVC_GEKHeTuDXkQt8YBKAF6BAgAEAY&amp;biw=895&amp;bih=370</a><br />\n<br />\n但click入去已經冇咗<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world-46627977\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fworld-46627977&d=bxRmApblJ2GFsDTLoFA1i26kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=1ee5a46e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fworld-46627977&h=8712415c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world-46627977</a>"},{"pid":"054be01093544e65046224746e57115330d3d383","tid":948250,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T01:59:10.000Z","msg":"你知道得太多了 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5544359e939d2f910daa3b31cf4140652db92aba","tid":948250,"uid":60977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T02:02:26.000Z","msg":"自主規制？"},{"pid":"d4c9c3dfad82a23717c1251cc9badaf5533952d0","tid":948250,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T02:28:22.000Z","msg":"香港失掉獨立關稅區地位的可能性<br />\n<br />\n...香港出口到美國的產品只有約34.6億港元，對出口影響算是輕微，香港甚少產品是完全依賴對美出口。香港科技大學經濟系教授雷鼎鳴接受BBC中文訪問時也形容，這些數字讓外界很容易就能評估美國取消視香港為獨立關稅區的影響。....<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/business-46589730\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fbusiness-46589730&d=bxRmApblJ2GFsDTLoFA1i26kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=6fa1b0e5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fbusiness-46589730&h=283670b9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/business-46589730</a><br />\n<br />\n成篇文好打手feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}